### 🧠 When to Use Which? 🤔

| Scenario | Choice | Why |
|----------|--------|-----|
| **Network requests** | `tokio::spawn` | Async I/O |
| **Database queries** | `tokio::spawn` | Async I/O |
| **File reading (async)** | `tokio::spawn` | Async I/O |
| **CPU-intensive work** | `spawn_blocking` | Doesn't block async runtime |
| **Blocking I/O** | `spawn_blocking` | File I/O, legacy libraries |
| **Image processing** | `spawn_blocking` | CPU-bound |
| **Encryption** | `spawn_blocking` | CPU-bound |
| **Legacy code** | `spawn_blocking` | Blocking APIs |

#### 🧠 The EVA Rule of Thumb ✨

