### 🧠 When to Use Broadcast Channels 🤔

| Scenario | Use Broadcast? | Why |
|----------|----------------|-----|
| **Real-time notifications** | ✅ Yes | Push updates to multiple clients |
| **Pub/Sub systems** | ✅ Yes | Fan-out messaging pattern |
| **Live dashboards** | ✅ Yes | Stream updates to multiple widgets |
| **Chat applications** | ✅ Yes | Distribute messages to all users |
| **System monitoring** | ✅ Yes | Broadcast metrics to multiple listeners |
| **Single consumer** | ❌ No | Use regular channels instead |
| **Ordered processing** | ❌ Maybe | Broadcast is lossy, may reorder |

