### 🧠 When to Use Which? 🤔

| Scenario | Choice | Why |
|----------|--------|-----|
| **Add one item** | `push` | Simple, clear intent |
| **Add multiple items** | `extend` | Efficient, works with iterators |
| **Building incrementally** | `push` | Natural for step-by-step building |
| **Adding from iterator** | `extend` | Designed for this use case |
| **Performance critical** | `extend` | Can pre-allocate memory |
| **Conditional additions** | `push` | Easy to conditionally add single items |

