### 🧠 When to Use HITL Bridge Pattern 🤔

| Scenario | Use Bridge? | Why |
|----------|-------------|-----|
| **Multiple systems need same approval** | ✅ Yes | Perfect fan-out use case |
| **Decoupled architecture** | ✅ Yes | Systems don't need to know each other |
| **Single source, multiple consumers** | ✅ Yes | Exactly what bridge provides |
| **Real-time notifications** | ✅ Yes | Efficient broadcast delivery |
| **Simple one-to-one communication** | ❌ No | Overhead not needed |
| **Performance-critical paths** | ❌ Maybe | Consider direct channels |

