### 🧠 When to Use MPSC to Broadcast Bridge 🤔

| Scenario | Use Bridge? | Why |
|----------|-------------|-----|
| **Multiple systems reacting to decision** | ✅ Yes | Fan-out communication |
| **Real-time dashboard updates** | ✅ Yes | Multiple UI clients |
| **Audit logging + processing + notifications** | ✅ Yes | Decoupled components |
| **Simple point-to-point communication** | ❌ No | Overhead not needed |
| **Single component processing** | ❌ No | MPSC sufficient |
| **Performance-critical paths** | ❌ Maybe | Consider overhead |

