### 🧠 When to Pause vs Error 🤔

| Scenario | Action | Reason |
|----------|--------|--------|
| **High-risk operation** | ✅ Pause | Human judgment needed |
| **Policy violation detected** | ✅ Error | System can decide |
| **Service temporarily down** | ✅ Error (retry) | Automatic recovery possible |
| **Invalid user input** | ✅ Error | Fix input to proceed |
| **Security violation** | ✅ Error (escalate) | Immediate attention required |
| **Complex edge case** | ✅ Pause | Human expertise valuable |
| **Configuration issue** | ✅ Error (escalate) | Admin intervention needed |

