### 🧠 When to Use done=true Fallback 🤔

| Scenario | Use done=true Fallback? | Why |
|----------|------------------------|-----|
| **Normal completion** | ✅ Yes | Ensures proper stream closure |
| **Early exit** | ✅ Yes | Prevents hanging streams |
| **Process crash** | ✅ Yes | Client needs to know stream ended |
| **Timeout** | ✅ Yes | Clean resource cleanup |
| **Shutdown** | ✅ Yes | Graceful termination |
| **Success only** | ❌ No | Not needed for success paths |

