| Scenario | Use done=true Fallback? | Why |
|----------|------------------------|-----|
| **Normal completion** | ✅ Yes | Ensures proper stream closure |
| **Process timeout** | ✅ Yes | Prevents hanging streams |
| **Process crash** | ✅ Yes | Client needs completion signal |
| **Output read error** | ✅ Yes | Graceful error handling |
| **Process wait failure** | ✅ Yes | Resource cleanup |
| **Shutdown** | ✅ Yes | Graceful termination |
| **Success only** | ❌ No | Not needed for clean paths |

