### 🧠 W3C Integration Best Practices 🤔

| Practice | Recommendation | Why |
|----------|----------------|-----|
| **Always Parse** | Parse W3C headers gracefully | Cross-system compatibility |
| **Validate Format** | Check hex format and lengths | Data integrity |
| **Respect Sampling** | Honor trace_flags sampling bit | Performance management |
| **Propagate Headers** | Forward headers to downstream | Trace continuity |
| **Handle Missing** | Create new traces when missing | Graceful degradation |
| **Sanitize Input** | Clean malformed headers | Security |
| **Log Integration** | Log trace IDs for correlation | Debugging |

