| Aspect | Session Span | Turn Span |
|--------|--------------|-----------|
| **Scope** | Entire user session | Individual interaction |
| **Lifetime** | Minutes to hours | Seconds to minutes |
| **Purpose** | Session context, metrics | Specific operation |
| **Children** | Turn spans | Sub-turn spans |
| **Analysis** | User behavior, trends | Performance, errors |
| **Storage** | Summary data | Detailed data |
| **Querying** | Cross-session patterns | Real-time operations |

